### Request an upload slot (requires auth cookie from auth.http)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/documents/upload
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "filename": "family-records.zip"
}

### Complete an upload (replace :id with the document_set_id from the slot response)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/documents/sets/:id/complete

### Poll the status of a document set
GET http://localhost:8080/api/documents/sets/:id
